			"styles": "\n\t/* escaped @ keeps its backslash (a bare @ would start an at-keyword) */\n\t@keyframes \\@mymove {\n\t\tfrom {\n\t\t\ttop: 0;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t/* escape mid-identifier is preserved */\n\t@keyframes a\\@b {\n\t\tfrom {\n\t\t\ttop: 0;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t/* hex escape with space terminator lets a name start with a digit */\n\t@keyframes \\31 23 {\n\t\tfrom {\n\t\t\ttop: 0;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n",
